{"tid":1997840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（歡迎狗仔討論）如果pk鄧落台，可唔可以平息民怨？","createTime":"2020-05-02T03:13:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T09:26:26.000Z","uid":264426,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1beaae3c18e11a7d3bb56833d8872ab1a9dc8592","tid":1997840,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:13:46.000Z","msg":"除非你班狗仔去反鄧生，拆佢台，否則pk鄧落台，你地都係過街老鼠。 <br />\n<br />\n就算pk自己落台，我地都對你班狗仔無好感。 想做正常人定過街老鼠，係你地班狗仔選擇，聲討自己老細我地都仲對你地有小小好感（頂多唔叫你地做狗），但遇著自己老細都唔敢屌，抵你班人做死一世狗"},{"pid":"b4abefb57a7187baa1658c00ed49a29780d04fc6","tid":1997840,"uid":83348,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:24:34.000Z","msg":"佢憑乜嘢，可以1個 = 3萬個仆街死黑警<br />\n<br />\n我唔單止要佢死，我仲要3萬仆街黑警一齊死<br />\n<br />\n仲要3萬個黑警家庭一齊家破人亡"},{"pid":"1a4f74c8c17eda4a3da0247210b626135b6d1c80","tid":1997840,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:25:52.000Z","msg":"落台炸喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢死嘅話都仲可以考慮一秒<br />\n都係不了"},{"pid":"d4552eefb84592abcabb510416e0510325fa18b6","tid":1997840,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:43:37.000Z","msg":"但係3萬反佢仲好過佢自己落台，問責落台根本落唔到佢面"},{"pid":"6a08a3b2883980dbe4eb69cd15d161308a5cb637","tid":1997840,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:44:04.000Z","msg":"而家pk係死要面炸"},{"pid":"3d0e361075e301fd8befc5a39cf689529eda9525","tid":1997840,"uid":3331,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:45:19.000Z","msg":"會呀！快啲啦！<br />\n唔係就會錯過同市民和解既機會！<br />\n把握機遇呀！"},{"pid":"988b4293bccac0d119865e8744628c550b29aee2","tid":1997840,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T04:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8961